<br /><strong>Total Price</strong>: 2.584,35 €</p>

<p>My thoughts on the list:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Great choices for quilt, shelter and pack</li>
  <li>Again a Exped SynMat UL 7, i probably would go for another one</li>
  <li>Sweet stove &amp; pot setup that’s very versatile</li>
  <li>Great choices for garments</li>
  <li>Overall a true UL list (although two items are missing) that’s under 5 kg, </li>
</ul>

